title: NOAA AHPS, Hurricane Ike rainfall totals for Sep 13, 2008 in selected counties along Gulf coast, USA, Sep 14, 2008
name: NOAA AHPS, Hurricane Ike rainfall totals for Sep 13, 2008 in selected counties along Gulf coast, USA, Sep 14, 2008
description: The point shapefile shows Hurricane Ike one day rainfall totals for selected counties along gulf coast for 14th Sep, 2008. The data consisting of nearly quarter million locations for the lower 48 states US was obtained from AHPS of NOAA and then extracted for 52 counties in the Gulf States that were most affected by Hurricane Ike.

author.source: NOAA's Advanceed Hydrologic Prediction Service (AHPS) website
